# Review Workflow Trigger

When the user says `/review`, asks to apply comments, or asks to iterate on a reviewed file:

1. Follow `.cursor/workflows/review.md`.
2. Identify the target file (ask only if ambiguous).
3. Fetch annotations using Review Mode MCP tools.
4. Implement requested changes in the file.
5. Resolve or update annotation statuses appropriately.
6. Re-open in Review Mode and report resolved versus pending items.
